title: #102: Operation AJAX with Maz Jobrani
description: Welcome to another fun festive episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode the boys welcome Pelvis aka Persian Elvis, Maz Jobrani, to talk the CIA's "Operation Ajax!"  Thank you for listening and we appreciate your support.
